{"tid":2333373,"cid":7,"subCid":0,"title":"E Cup Baby劉欣宜轉做空姐七年 發文控訴無理解僱","createTime":"2020-12-20T10:41:15.000Z","updateTime":"2020-12-20T13:38:00.000Z","uid":147522,"like":7,"dislike":7,"uniUserReply":23,"replies":[{"pid":"c3ec398378117ca0413966c821082977dbb86ac8","tid":2333373,"uid":147522,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-20T10:41:15.000Z","msg":"曾經在𡃁模界叱吒一時的E Cup Baby劉欣宜，當年憑34E上圍吸納無數宅男粉絲，後來𡃁模沒落她亦收山，13年退出娛樂圈轉型做空中服務員，可惜過去一年因疫情關係航空業大受影響，繼早前港龍航空結業，香港航空亦宣布裁走250名機組人員。收到大信封的E Cup Baby不忿被裁，在社交網出post大控訴，表示自己盡忠職守七年最後得到這個結果，感到非常之失望。<br />\n<br />\n𡃁模出身的E Cup Baby劉欣宜，近年在娛樂圈消聲匿跡，原來已轉投空中服務員工作，她由普通艙服務員做起，任職七年已進升成為Purser（座艙長）級別，可惜一場疫情令她加入失業大軍。香港航空宣布要裁員250人，E Cup Baby亦收到大信封，她在社交網發文，表示已收到公司解僱信，令她感到突然兼不是味兒&hellip;&hellip;她指自己做過幾年best cabin crew（最佳乘務員）、由FA（空中服務員）做到purser。從來無過錯，只有功勞，而且她幫公司執過屎、執過舊機、捱過困獸鬥又入team，Outport陪crew入醫院都唔只一次。<br />\n<br />\n睇到這裡已經知道E Cup Baby效力的一肚苦水，對於自己被解僱表示極度不忿，她自問七年來盡忠職守，而收大信封前一晚剛落機，為此她表示其實完全冇諗過會係自己，主要係失望同唔捨得。雖然感到失望，但E Cup Baby仍感謝一直以來與她飛過的同事同朋友：「令我每班機都好開心、好難忘。留低嘅要繼續努力。不過再一次證明原來炒人真係同performance（表現）無關。咁&hellip;&hellip;我啲獎算係乜？」 <br />\n<br />\n突然失業的E Cup Baby已經31 歲，她於16年下嫁音樂人陳子敏，前年誕下一女，2歲半的囡囡活潑可愛，E Cup Baby不時在社交網上載生活照，一家三口生活得幸福快樂，E Cup Baby更煮得一手好菜，唔做空姐大不了做個全職媽媽。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/BZjtv90.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FBZjtv90.png&h=cbb7abfe&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2020/12/20/184105_fcdfaefdebd3bb7e03c2307c190dad97.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2020%2F12%2F20%2F184105_fcdfaefdebd3bb7e03c2307c190dad97.png&h=ce8e58cc&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2020/12/20/184107_15c9d6411db04e34f58c95fa2ed21a69.jpeg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2020%2F12%2F20%2F184107_15c9d6411db04e34f58c95fa2ed21a69.jpeg&h=fdf8c43b&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2020/12/20/184107_494e98df33a19111f0f40485e645c586.jpeg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2020%2F12%2F20%2F184107_494e98df33a19111f0f40485e645c586.jpeg&h=8e30d1cd&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2020/12/20/184108_d4e3f8b0f1756841209802c04294c377.jpeg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2020%2F12%2F20%2F184108_d4e3f8b0f1756841209802c04294c377.jpeg&h=f783bce2&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"be6d9b4f3a4e0266475f1e07d9c57687ae7cba96","tid":2333373,"uid":38904,"like":8,"dislike":1,"score":7,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-12-20T10:43:54.000Z","msg":"她指自己做過幾年best cabin crew（最佳乘務員）<br />\n<br />\n同中學最佳學生有乜嘢分別<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7e9a4df7e32fc5539c860f4de1ae00690db74e94","tid":2333373,"uid":47492,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-20T10:44:14.000Z","msg":"垃圾"},{"pid":"4ffd354e69681a7ef327c2fa4f382e4e38047f4d","tid":2333373,"uid":99700,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-20T10:45:18.000Z","msg":"全職主婦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c52b1721e691139927fee8667d5e46ee12b6e9ab","tid":2333373,"uid":24591,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-20T10:46:30.000Z","msg":"幾錢q<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/touch.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/touch.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f0ad60ddc59f120b6883bc618af75cdc4cbf1695","tid":2333373,"uid":228143,"like":0,"dislike":3,"score":-3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-20T10:48:26.000Z","msg":"又刷存在感"},{"pid":"8763759765a4b23a18778685307d2acb163eb81b","tid":2333373,"uid":149494,"like":9,"dislike":1,"score":8,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-12-20T10:48:54.000Z","msg":"呢d真係好似第一日出黎做嘢咁<br />\n任何行業任何公司唔掂嗰陣都會炒人架啦<br />\n你既價值唔係特別重要嗰個咪無得留低囉<br />\n講到欠撚咗佢咁"},{"p